				<h1 class="shead-style text-center">TRIPURA</h1>
				<p>Resting in the northeastern region Tripura is the third smallest in India. Previously ruled by many rulers and dynasties Tripura gives the touch of culturally strong and vibrant place. Separated far from Indiaâ€™s popular tourist circuit it awaits people with a welcoming heart and culture. Tripura which has a number of royal palaces and temples requires no special permit for any kind of tourists.</p><p> 
        A mountainous state Tripura can be visited within a short period of time due to its smaller size. The culture and tradition of Tripura reflects its daily life and society.
        </p>
